B2B Commerce: MercadoLibre launches new B2B unit to tap corporate market

🌎 MercadoLibre has announced the launch of a new B2B unit, strengthening its position as Latin America’s leading e-commerce provider by targeting corporate clients.
🏢 This division focuses on supplying businesses and organizations with tailored digital solutions—moving beyond its traditional consumer marketplace.
💼 The initiative unlocks new growth opportunities, as companies in the region seek more efficient procurement platforms and integrated buying experiences.
🚀 By expanding into the B2B space, MercadoLibre aims to leverage its technology and logistics network to serve the unique needs of the corporate market.
🔍 This move reflects a broader industry trend, with e-commerce giants evolving to become central hubs for both consumer and business purchasing.
